{"tid":193831,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好撚憎in-app browser","createTime":"2017-04-09T14:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T17:26:25.000Z","uid":46064,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d97190eeb282e0d3cac0815693de66c5db89bb7e","tid":193831,"uid":46064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"宜家每個app開link都硬係要整個in-app browser<br />\n即係app入面click link唔係開safari, chrome<br />\n係直接喺個app入面開頁browser出黎<br />\n<br />\n雖然一開始個用意係幾好可以唔使轉app都睇到網頁<br />\n但記唔到login就係死罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到成日都要入完個page要再選返用browser開<br />\n用緊數據上網既真係多得你唔少又要load多次個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最撚慘係有D app係根本冇選項比你熄左呢個功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚心你做唔到browser既基本功能不如就咪撚整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2c9b7d0115bb4c0d05791845922b7452920320","tid":193831,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"以前成日比人屌係咁跳safari<br />\n<br />\n而家又比人屌in-app<br />\n<br />\n好難服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d468d8be79af5f9860742c6626158e47c69345","tid":193831,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前成日比人屌係咁跳safari<br />\n<br />\n而家又比人屌in-app<br />\n<br />\n好難服侍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有d app in app browser好撚廢<br />\n好似以前hkg+"},{"pid":"40b4a9338c2079814f8cb5ce7b7606b6143cad29","tid":193831,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"我都覺， 我android有app可以做到floating browser效果， 唔洗轉app既 但而家要用in app browser再開"}]}